Fix Bad AI Speeches

You need to write a toast for your boss at a team retreat. You ask the AI for a heartfelt speech. It gives you vague phrases like celebrate hard work and amazing journey. The clock is ticking. The AI keeps giving you awkward or cliché phrases.

Here's the fix:
AI works best when you tell it exactly what mistakes to avoid. Don’t just ask for a good speech. Tell it to skip specific problems like clichés or vague praise. (1/3)
